*  N. G. Ranga
* Yadlapati Venkata Rao
* Gouthu Latchanna
* Chowdary Satyanarayana
* Villuri Venkataramana
* N. V. Rama Rao
* Kandula Obul Reddy
* Paturi Rajagopala Naidu
* Bharati Devi Ranga
