==== Section Coztomatae ====

* &quot;Physalis aggregata&quot; 
* &quot;Physalis angustior&quot; 
* &quot;Physalis chenopodifolia&quot; 
* &quot;Physalis coztomatl&quot; 
* &quot;Physalis greenmanii&quot; 
* &quot;Physalis hintonii&quot; 
